<br>
I personally have never shown a false picture of myself to anyone. I'm not sure why anyone would. If someone wants to see me I give them my web page address and go tell them to take a look. If they start ignoring me cos they don't like what they see -- then I guess they weren't my friend in the first place *shrug*<br>
