If you're not going to be meeting in RL, or starting something there folks, what is wrong with continuing to have fun with someone online, if you enjoy their company, despite their apearance? For that matter, what is wrong with meeting that person and at least being friends, even if it doesn't cross the line into relationship or sex? *shrugs*<br>
